\"text-indent:37px;line-height:33px\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">（三）参赛队员一律穿足球鞋（禁止使用金属钉）、佩戴护腿板、穿足球长袜、着统一颜色服装、号码位置正确清晰，否则不予上场比赛。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:37px;line-height:33px\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">（四）比赛采用国家总体育局审定的最新竞赛规则。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:37px;line-height:33px\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">（五）比赛无越位限制，角球和任意门可直接射门得分。累计连续</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;background-color: white\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">张黄牌停赛</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;background-color: white\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">场，</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;background-color: white\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">张红牌停赛</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;background-color: white\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">场，红、黄牌累计带入下一阶段。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:37px;line-height:33px\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">（六）视参赛队队数，比赛采用分组循环或交叉赛制等进行。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:37px;line-height:33px\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">（七）全场比赛</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;background-color: white\">40</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">分钟，上、下半场各</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;background-color: white\">15</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">分钟，中场休息</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;background-color: white\">10</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">分钟</span></p><p style=\"line-height:33px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">决定名次办法：</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent:37px;line-height:33px\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">（一）胜</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;background-color: white\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">场得</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;background-color: white\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">分，平</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;background-color: white\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">场各得</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;background-color: white\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">分，负</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;background-color: white\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">场得</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;background-color: white\">0</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">分，积分多者名列前，弃权</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;background-color: white\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">场取消全部成绩。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:37px;line-height:33px\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">（二）必须决出胜负的比赛成平局，采用互踢点球决定胜负。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:37px;line-height:33px\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">（三）如遇两队或两队以上积分相等，则按下列顺序决定名次</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;background-color: white\">:</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:37px;line-height:33px\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;background-color: white\">A</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">．积分相等队相互之间比赛的胜者名次列前；</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:37px;line-height:33px\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;background-color: white\">B</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">．积分相等队相互之间比赛的净胜球多者名次列前；</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:37px;line-height:33px\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;background-color: white\">C</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">．积分相等队相互之间比赛的进球总和多者名次列前；</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:37px;line-height:33px\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;background-color: white\">D</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">．积分相等队相互之间比赛的红、黄牌总和少者名次列前；</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:37px;line-height:33px\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;background-color: white\">E</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">．如仍相等，则采用抽签的办法决定名次。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:9px;line-height:33px\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">录取名次及奖励办法：</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent:37px;line-height:33px\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">（一）各年纪组录取前</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;background-color: white\">6</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">名，不足</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;background-color: white\">6</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">个队减</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;background-color: white\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">录取</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:37px;line-height:33px\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">（二）各组别前</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;background-color: white\">6</span><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">名给予奖励；</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:37px\"><span style=\"font-size: 19px;font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;background-color: white\">（三）各组别设体育道德风尚奖一名。</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><br/></p>','46');
